Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,575)}离婚成功的终极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1233,646)}凭此广告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202,670)}侦探委托费零元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,694)}婚外恋调查费零元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(499,195)}什么时候都可以应对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,368)}免费咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(67,181)}婚外恋调查
