Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:55.65,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是这样  当数不清的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:00.65,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.75,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:10.03,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.68,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.07,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:20.79,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:27.00,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:32.07,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:37.23,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:41.97,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:46.67,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:52.39,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.77,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:57.25,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:00.49,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}为明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:05.23,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}命名
